{title: I Am Resolved}
{artist: Jamie Dailey and Darrin Vincent}
{composer: Written by Lewis Hartsough and Gary Lanier}

[C]I am resolved no [F]longer to linger
[C]Charmed by the world's [G7]delight
[C]Things that are higher
[F]Things that are nobler
[C]These have [G7]allured my [C]sight
I will [F]hasten to Him [C]hasten so glad and [G7]free
[C]Jesus [F]greatest highest [C]I will [G7]come to [C]Thee
I am resolved to [F]go to the Savior
[C]Leaving my sin and [G7]strife
[C]He is the true one
[F]He is the just one
[C]He hath the [G7]words of [C]life
Repeat #2

I am resolved to [F]follow the Savior
[C]Faithful and true each [G7]day
[C]Heed what He sayeth [F]do what He willeth
[C]He is the [G7]living [C]way
Repeat #2